column2: SELECT n.objid, m.rmapid, m.ra as ra, m.dec as dec, s.z as z_spec, m.z_lambda as zlambda, o.deVRad_r, o.deVAB_r, o.deVPhi_r, n.distance, m.lambda as lambda, m.mstar as mstar, m.p_cen0 as p_cen,    m.Dn4#,m.MtoLz, m.logAge,m.Metal into mydb.MyTable_radius from myDB.redmapper_mstar as m     cross apply dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(m.ra, m.dec, #) as n     join Galaxy as o on n.objid=o.objID          join SpecObj as s on n.objid=s.bestobjID
